name: AI Avatar #133 (The Golden Empress)
description:
"That was perhaps the first time I was completely awestruck by what I saw. Her eyes are Golden, accompanied by a Peach blush on her cheeks. Silver hair with streaks of Gold flow around her face while a veil-like Golden aura emanates from her visage. She wears a Black robe, which contrasts starkly with its intricate Gold trimmings. Any man who lays eyes on her would not have a single doubt, that he is now in the presence of … The Golden Empress."

---

This Avatar was created using an AI (Generative Adversarial Network) over countless iterations, with the goal of achieving the Pinnacle of Human Beauty. Just as each Human is unique, each Avatar is Forever Unique. Each Avatar will only be minted once and there will be no copies.
